# ----- Multi-operator (see README → "Multi-operator deployment") -----
# Two recipes: same-host N nodes for screenshots, multi-host for prod.
# Key invariant: deploy QUORUM_NUM/QUORUM_DEN on the oracle AND
# THRESHOLD_NUM/THRESHOLD_DEN on the security contract together.
# E.g. 5 operators at 4-of-5:
#   QUORUM_NUM=4 QUORUM_DEN=5 task deploy-oracle
#   THRESHOLD_NUM=4 THRESHOLD_DEN=5 task set-threshold
